    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/exceptions-to-the-moratorium-on-discretionary-spend"/>
    <title>Exceptions to the moratorium on discretionary spend</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;h2 id="background"&gt;Background&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The government has introduced a strict moratorium in 5 key areas of discretionary spend:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;consulting&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Information and communications technology (ICT)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;recruitment&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;marketing  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;property &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Exceptions to the moratoria in key areas are listed in documents.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
