&lt;p&gt;Information broken down by: Rail sector&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="latest-data"&gt;Latest data&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passengers travelled 8.9 billion miles by rail in the first quarter of 2012-13, an increase of 3% when compared to the same quarter in 2011-12. These figures are for franchised operators only, so exclude travel with non-franchised operators, such as Grand Central, Heathrow Express and Hull Trains.&lt;/li&gt;
